---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Daycare Marketing Strategies | Childcare Business Plan"
    description="Discover effective daycare marketing strategies tailored to your local market competition and saturation levels."
>
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
        <!-- 1. OWNERSHIP FRAMING -->
        <section class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                YOUR enrollment growth
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                True growth comes from understanding that your center is a
                unique brand in your community, not just another option on the
                list.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 2. FACTORS THAT AFFECT OUTCOME -->
        <section class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                What Affects Your Marketing Success
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Your ability to fill spots depends heavily on local market
                saturation, the specific demographics of families in your
                radius, and the intensity of competition nearby. What works in a
                dense urban center will fail in a suburban setting.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 3. WHY GENERIC ADVICE FAILS -->
        <section class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                Why Online Advice Often Conflicts
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Marketing gurus often push expensive digital ads that may not
                reach your specific local parents. Your marketing plan needs to
                be built around your specific location and capacity goals,
                focusing on high-conversion local channels rather than broad,
                expensive campaigns.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 4. CTA TO CALCULATOR -->
        <section
            class="text-center py-12 px-8 glass-panel rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                See How Much YOU Could Make in Your State
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Get your personalized income estimate based on your state's
                regulations to understand your revenue potential.
            </p>
            <a
                href="/tools/income-builder"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-medium px-8 py-4 shadow-lg transition-all"
            >
                Use the Free Calculator →
            </a>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
